                     go to inc-rec-let-500
           else      go to inc-rec-let-999.
       inc-rec-let-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se maggiore di 10                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      f-xxx-nrl            to   f-xxx-nrd              .
           if        f-xxx-nrd            =    zero
